-- Lehman to unveil strategic plan next week: media
-- 
-- Tue Sep 9, 2008 5:28am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/09/us-lehman-idUSSEL00024720080909

 

 SEOUL  (Reuters) - Lehman Brothers is set to hold a conference call on September 18 to discuss its third-quarter earnings and "key strategic initiatives for the firm", the Web site of Fortune magazine reported on Tuesday, citing Lehman. 

 "Lehman didn't offer any details on either count, other than to say it will issue a press release after the market closes next Thursday and hold the (conference) call at 4:30 p.m. Eastern time," Fortune reported. (Reporting by Kim Yeon-hee; Editing by Keiron Henderson)